  "description": "Resource Pack add Dark Theme in Modified Minecraft",
  "body": "<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1019762/description_f72665c9-2084-471b-9903-ee3f4e73da46.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"850\" height=\"467\" /></p>\n<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</h1>\n<h1 style=\"justify-content: center;\">The Dark Theme For Mods</h1>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h4 style=\"text-align: center;\">Enhance your Minecraft experience with the Dark Mode + Mods pack,</h4>\n<h4 style=\"text-align: center;\">which applies a sleek dark theme to all inventories in Industrial Craft 2 and other major mods.</h4>\n<h1>&nbsp;</h1>\n<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\">Support</h1>\n<h6 style=\"text-align: center;\">Write your sugestion about next mod in:&nbsp;<a href=\"https://github.com/laur221/dark-theme\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">GitHub</a></h6>\n<h6 style=\"text-align: center;\">My patreon with news about resource pack: &nbsp;<a href=\"https://patreon.com/DarkModeforModeResourcePack\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Patreon</a></h6>\n<h6 style=\"text-align: center;\">For support and inspiration that not everything is done in vain: &nbsp;<a href=\"https://ko-fi.com/darktheme\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Ko-fi</a></h6>\n<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</h1>\n<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\">Mods Support</h1>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/ae2\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Applied Energistics</a> - ✅</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/industrial-craft\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Industrial Craft 2</a> - ✅</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/jei\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Just Enough Items</a> - ✅</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/thermal-expansion\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Thermat Expansion</a> - ✅</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/thermal-dynamics\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Thermal Dynamics</a> - ✅</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/thaumcraft\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Thaumcraft</a> - ✅</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/botania\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Botania</a> - ✅</p>",
